{"tid":797580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：少林寺歷史性升中國國旗 建寺1523年首次","createTime":"2018-08-28T15:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T23:51:44.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8922872e0aabaa28adf1e0db189a93722116847d","tid":797580,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2147433/佛門要愛國%20少林寺「歷史性」升五星旗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2147433%2F%E4%BD%9B%E9%96%80%E8%A6%81%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%2520%E5%B0%91%E6%9E%97%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7%E3%80%8D%E5%8D%87%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E6%97%97&d=1QkAAHUoEfx2rceYaHtwY9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=53bdd4e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2147433/佛門要愛國%20少林寺「歷史性」升五星旗</a><br />\n<br />\n創建於北魏太和19年（公元495年）的河南嵩山少林寺，今天上午7時在方丈釋永信率領下，舉行建寺1523年來首度的升旗典禮， 於山門外升起五星紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n少林寺官網稱，在宗教活動場所升掛國旗與少林寺堅持「愛國愛教」的主題思想吻合。少林寺率先做出表態，希望廣大宗教界人士和信教群眾不斷增強尊重國旗、愛護國旗、維護國旗的尊嚴意識，牢固樹立法制觀念，把法治精神融入到宗教實踐和宗教生活中去。<br />\n<br />\n建寺1523年來 首度舉行升旗典禮<br />\n<br />\n今年7月31日，全國性宗教團體聯席會議第六次會議在京舉行，發出《關於在宗教活動場所升掛國旗的倡議》。8月15日，中國佛教協會九屆三次理事會在北京召開，學習並回應這項《倡議》。少林寺很快就響應，方丈釋永信更積極表態稱，要率先在嵩山少林寺行動起來。"},{"pid":"a3a3ffc5f77ed5f2c9e6e80c5b59a0907ed08b46","tid":797580,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"中共既力量比少林寺十八銅人仲要大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ddb3ba25d91e64356770ea13c9bb87ae8bf447","tid":797580,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"一盤生意"},{"pid":"54ffe3907c3cc04a9126e791e0a9a135ebabe51b","tid":797580,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05898064fc0353eb4fc3a34606bea5d9b57a3d95","tid":797580,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"超越毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562e089dc46dcd28facbe8349b961dfe83c5bdbf","tid":797580,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be19cb309c229ab2491397d005523d223b1f56c1","tid":797580,"uid":135217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"自古以來<br />\n共產黨就擁有了少林寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aee9c81b27cb9c99ce8279452aba4fd7dc1edba","tid":797580,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"維穩搖錢樹<br />\n明鏡照橫財<br />\n時時唱國歌<br />\n荷包冇塵埃"},{"pid":"6df87ec32c09f25626bff0d500f6ddb9bb74a68e","tid":797580,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T23:49:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"86de959b13f005e14a221c9a7a1ae40a0518548c","tid":797580,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"全真教..."}]}